{"word":"ἀναπλέω","slug":"ἀναπλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναπλέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to sail up, to go up stream</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to put out to sea</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sail the same way back again, sail back</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—of fish, <i>to swim back</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}